expression: normalized
---
Search skills by query with explicit scope flags (remote default)

Usage: fastskill search [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>  Search query string

Options:
      --local                    Search local/installed skills only
      --remote                   Search remote skill catalogs (default, can be explicit for scripts)
      --repository <REPOSITORY>  Limit remote search to specific repository (remote scope only)
  -l, --limit <LIMIT>            Maximum number of results (default: 10) [default: 10]
  -f, --format <FORMAT>          Output format: table, json, grid, xml (default: table)
      --json                     Shorthand for --format json
      --embedding <EMBEDDING>    Use embedding search: true, false, or auto Only applies to local search; ignored for remote search [possible values: true, false, auto]
  -h, --help                     Print help

Examples:
  fastskill search "text processing"
  fastskill search "text processing" --local
  fastskill search "pptx" --repository my-repo
  fastskill search "query" -l 5 --json
